            <h1 class="rev-title-inner text-start" id="online-main-title">Online Coaching Program</h1>
            <p>In the online coaching program, I build you a complete, challenging, and personalized training plan that you can do anywhere, anytime that works for you! Based entirely on your schedule.</p>
            <p>The plan is built and tailored to the number of days you can train per week and the time you have for each session. <br>
            For example: a 3-day-per-week plan with 2 sessions of 40-60 minutes and one 30-minute session.</p>
            <p>In every plan, each exercise includes a link to my YouTube channel with demonstration videos and detailed explanations on proper form &mdash; these will always be available to you.<br>
            With them, we'll work on technique and go over the important cues for each exercise.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block single">
            <h2 class="rev-title-inner text-start" id="online-sub-1">Documenting Your Workouts</h2>
            <p>So I can track your progress in the best possible way, all you need to do is film yourself performing a few reps of each exercise.<br>
            Upload the clips to a dedicated shared folder I'll set up for us.</p>
            <p>After reviewing the footage, I'll write notes, comments, and cues for each exercise. This way we'll improve technique, progress from session to session, and build strength and confidence.</p>
        </div>

